org.rapla.plugin.dhbwscheduler.server

Class ConstraintService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rapla.plugin.dhbwscheduler.server.ConstraintService

  • public class ConstraintService
extends java.lang.Object
    Constraint Service provides methods for building, changing and getting data from the constraints of the docents. The constraints are created in following form: 0: DozentID 1: Constraints 2: Dates 3: Status DOZID_000000000000000000000000...111111111111111111111111_ExceptionDate,ExceptionDate_Status\n DOZID_000000000000000000000000...111111111111111111111111_ExceptionDate,ExceptionDate_Status

      • changeDozConstraint

        public static java.lang.String changeDozConstraint(java.lang.String constraint,
                                   java.lang.String doz_ID,
                                   int changevalue,
                                   java.lang.Object[] value)
        changes the docent-constraint, depending on the changevalue. changevalue = 1 = changes single constraint changevalue = 2 = changes single dates changevalue = 3 = changes single status the value of the parameter value is used for the change and the docent-constraint is created with buildDozConst
        Parameters:
        constraint - full constraint of all docents as string
        doz_ID - ID of the docent
        changevalue - change-mode
        value - new value after change
        Returns:
        changedConstraint
